ll see\n(你會看到)\nHere we are\n(我們在這裡)\n\nchase down the brightest light\n(就追逐最亮的光前進吧)\n\nBridge：\nAim to the sky\n(瞄準天空)\nYou can risk it, try it, don’t be scared to cry\n(就去冒險、嘗試吧，別害怕的哭泣)\nHa~ Smile to yourself\n(啊〜對著自己微笑吧)\nYou will be fine\n(你會一直好好的喔)\n\nChorus1：\nDon’t let them put you down\n(別讓他們令你沮喪)\nThey can’t hurt us as long as we stay strong\n(他們不能傷害我們，只要我們保持堅強)\nIt’s a life of Rock N Roll\n(這是搖滾的生活)\nWe may struggle, may fall, but still going forward\n(我們也許會掙扎著、也許會跌倒，但還是會向前邁進)\nWho says we can’t make it to the end\n(是誰說我們不能堅持到底呢)\nIf you believe it\n(如果你相信)\n\nChorus2：\nDo you really know the reason why?\n(你真的知道原因嗎？)\nCome sing a song for me\n(唱著一首給自己的歌)\nOur hearts will tell us where we should be\n(心將告訴我們前進的方向)\nIt’s a life of rock N Roll\n(這是場搖滾的生活)\nWe are dreaming, living, waiting to begin\n(我們做著夢、生活著、等待著開始)\nEvery step of the way is worth it\n(每一步都是值得的喔)\nDon’t look away\n(不要把目光移開)\nYou will see\n(你將會看到)\nHere we are\n(我們在這裡)', 256, '尋找愛麗絲', '', '', '', 'White Pony Music Studio', '', 1, 0, 0, '2014-05-07 21:08:48', '2015-03-12 14:07:03', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
